"1 1/2 pounds cauliflower, trimmed and cut into florets","3/4 cup chopped bottled roasted red bell peppers (about 4 ounces)","1/2 cup thinly sliced red onion","1/2 cup coarsely chopped fresh flat-leaf parsley","1/2 cup coarsely chopped green olives (about 2 ounces)","1/4 teaspoon crushed red pepper","1  large celery rib, sliced crosswise","2 tablespoons extra-virgin olive oil","1 tablespoon fresh lemon juice","1 tablespoon white wine vinegar","1/2 teaspoon black pepper","1/8 teaspoon sea salt","1.5 ounces provolone piccante, cut into small pieces","  Celery leaves (optional)"